<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DishDiscovery</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css\style.css">
    <script src="script.js"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        td{
            border: 2px solid white;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
            border-collapse:collapse;
        }
        th{
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        table{
            display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width:100% ;
        }
        h1, h2{
            margin: 2%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p{
            padding: 2%;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="loginn">
    <%- include("../shared/head") %>
    <div class="content">
        <h1>Welcome,  Pratham!</h1>
        <h2>Welcome to Favourites Section</h2>
        <p>Welcome to DishDiscovery, your ultimate destination for discovering and saving delicious recipes! Whether you're a seasoned chef or just starting out in the kitchen, our platform offers a wide range of mouthwatering recipes for every taste and occasion.</p>
        <p>By saving your favorite recipes to your profile, you can easily access them anytime, anywhere. No more searching through countless websites or flipping through cookbooks â€“ your favorite recipes are just a click away!</p>
        <section class="recipes">
            <h2>Here are the recipes that you have added to favorites:</h2>
            <table>
                
                    <tr>
                        <th>Favourites</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Spaghetti Carbonara</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Margherita Pizza</td>
                    </tr>
                
                    <% favourites.forEach(function(favorite) { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><%= favorite.recipe.title %></td>
                            <td><a href="#" class="delete-btn">Delete</a></td>
                        </tr>
                    <% }); %>
                
            </table>
            <div class="additional-info">
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> You can find the detailed ingredients and instructions for each recipe in your favorites section. Enjoy cooking!</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
<%- include("../shared/footer") %>
</html>
